Sorry I haven't been around for a while. I've been <small><strike>sneaking off to Soul Society</small></strike>rather busy and didn't have access to my computer. It was rather short-notice, so I didn't have time to put up a prior message. No need to worry, though. I'm back now~

I doubt Oomaeda will be throwing you a party, so why don't you come here? [/Private] ((OOC: Yes, that myu clip is SUBBED! It's the opening to Dark of the Bleeding Moon~ *__*))

Hello everyone! Shihouin Yoruichi here. Previous leader of the Onmitsu Kidou and heiress to the Shihouin family, one of the Four Noble Families in Seireitei.

...Ah. I see an Espada has made it's way into Brawl. Interesting.
Yo! Sorry I haven't been around in a while. I've... been neglecting the internet for a while. I come bearing a few icons! From Kingdom Hearts II. 1. 2. 3. 4. 5.

So after god knows how long of trying to figure out what to do for my second clue, I finally figured it out, and I have aquired my final clue: ....What? Must...resist...urge...to...use...shunko.... ((OOC: If anyone is curious about Yoruichi aquiring her last clue, let's just say there was a map that came with it, which led to the pool of pudding(ftw?) where the clue was. I'm sorry, but I've been a bit busy getting Hinamori introduced into BNF and things like that. I promise not to neglect Yoru-chan ever again. D: ))

I finally got my second clue from that Michael Jackson guy. ....I swear, that guy is creepy. He just kept smiling at me. One of those weird, unnerving smiles, Like Aizen's.. SO I just took the damn clue and left. As quickly as possible. dfskjhsdfklhdkfj I am THIS CLOSE TO USING SHUNKO RIGHT NOW FG;LKJSD;LGKDJFS;LFG ...Okay. ....wtf? ....Does it have something to do with twins? OI, HITACHIIN. WEASLEY. Do either of you have my next clue?

AFter having a (very short) conversation with it seems I have to go to Neverland to aquire my next clue. ...No. Not that Neverland. That wouldn't be sadistic. It would be un-Mary-like. ...I guess I'm off to visit Michael Jackson. ..... Uuuuuuuugh. God, help me.

Urahara, you better stop answering questions about me. Direct everyone here if they ask any more. Ask me a question about anything--fandom, real life, music,vegetables, etc--and I will answer you and then ask YOU a question andthen the whole process could be repeated if anyone wants to keep it up.If this works, by the end we could know each other so well we're sick of each other and have to quit one another for a while.

Okay, obviously my fic pissed some people off. let me clear some things up:

1. I do not hate Hitsugaya.
2. I did not intend to hurt him in any way.
3. It a free world. I can post whatever I please, damnit.
4. I would like the comments to be POSITIVE. if you've got nothing nice to say. shut your damn mouth and don't say it at all.

<small>((OOC: Thanks for killing my self-esteem, guys.))</small>

...Interesting. It seems many people are turning into kittens. Well, I don't see what the big deal is. Being a cat is no problem for me. It's quite fun. Though I suppose the situations are complately diffrent...

I decided to take the meme that's been floating around lately...

The Random Question Meme!

An array of completely random questions about my friends!

What hobby do you think should take up?
It seems they have enough hobbies as it is.
Where do you think is right now?
Dunno. Home? Practicing tennis somewhere?
Does understand quantum chromodynamics?
I highly doubt it.
What animal does most remind you of?
A little bee ^_^!
What's the last thing you said to ?
...Nothing.
What is 's religion?
....Any religion that could possibly make her smarter.
Does look better with long hair?
Yes~ Of course, I've only seen her with long hair...
How many people has seduced?
How am I supposed to know that...?
What is 's favorite meal?
Blood, of course.
What would you say at 's funeral?
...Who?
What will be like in twenty years?
..Hmm? Sorry, don't know who that is...
What do you most envy about ?
Nothing, really.

This is by . You can find your own completely random questions here.

Do you feel enlightened now?

Have any of you ever had a dream where your loved one dies right in front of you, and you can't do anything about it?

It's a scary thought, really. I've never had one of those dreams until last night. I haven't been able to get back to sleep since...Don't get me wrong, I usually have no problem sleeping. It's just that dream kept nagging me, and the idea wouldn't leave me alone.

I've been feeling a bit under the weather today, for no reason I know of. I guess the sudden change in weather has something to do with it.

I got a few things off my chest this week, and I'm glad I did......

Anyway...moving on...I've been looking through Urahara's CDs, and I found one from a musical called "Sweeney Todd." Anyone ever heard of it? It's about a psycho barber that slit the throats of his customers, and his partner in crime bakes them into pies. And sells them.

....Hey, it sounds better then it is.
I have a new goal in life... ....Annoy Atobe until he snaps. Who's with me~? Edit: Haruhi thinks we should also annoy Axel until he cracks. Anyone up for that too?

Yo~ Shihouin Yoruichi here. Goddess of Flash, Supreme Commander, Yoruichi-sama...whatever. ((If anyone calls me Yoru-chan, I swear I'll kill you.))

For those of you who don't know me, I am a Shinigami. And I can transform into a cat. So don't be surprised of that happens from time to time. I tend to suffer from fits of incurable boredom.

Hmm...I think I'll go say hello to a certain Little Bee~
